        {
            "title": "大舉入市｜施永青基金820萬買太古城兩房 半年斥資1.4億掃10層樓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.v2n_BuwbRx71P3CaouW9Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc4OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/14d4f3ddcf7d2e833c10a0c67a0968d6\" width=\"685\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年發表港樓見底論的中原集團創辦人<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"施永青\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:施永青;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/施永青\">施永青</a>旗下基金又買樓，以820萬元購入鰂魚涌太古城一個實用面積582方呎的兩房單位，連同去年10月至今，過去近半年，斥資1.4億元購入10層港樓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資料顯示，太古城高山台天山閣低層H室，實用面積582方呎，本月初以820萬元易手，呎價14,089元，成交價較銀行估價低約2.2%。買家為FIFE INVESTMENT LIMITED﹐股東為施永青基金，董事包括中原集團創辦人施永青。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-16cb810a-d2db-3f91-b3e3-7a12596c28ff-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">翻查資料，施永青旗下基金FIFE INVESTMENT LIMITED，自去年10月起，不斷掃貨，包括何文田瑜一、九龍站擎天半島、大角咀柏景灣、西環翰林峰、泓都、上環荷李活道等等，連同今次太古城單位，去年底至今已斥資近1.4億元掃10層港樓。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">施永青去年11月撰文，確認本港住宅樓已確認見底回升，預期上升浪可持續6年，由2025年升至2031年，與去年3月的低位相比，升幅可達85%。</p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://lgltdclass.com/ken_freeclassreg_bmyt/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q0yPB1bneLQ4ikXCxrf7.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/ae6af5ac577c6b197341c289fcb33169\" width=\"900\"/></div></a></div>",
